Title: KPZ Formulas for Weyl-Invariant Induced Gravity and Topologically

Massive GravityAuthors: G. Amelino-Camelia

Comments: 4 pages, LaTex. (Contribution to the Proceedings of the 2nd Topical

Meeting on Constrained Dynamics and Quantum Gravity.)Journal-ref: Nucl.Phys.Proc.Suppl. 57 (1997) 276-279

I discuss the applicability in Weyl-invariant induced gravity andtopologically massive gravity of certain formulas originally derived byKnizhnik, Polyakov, and Zamolodchikov in the context ofdiffeomorphism-invariant induced gravity.